snippet.title: Skator Gator 3D: Day Level Teaser
snippet.description:
Greenjamin makes the jump to 3D in Skator Gator 3D, the upcoming sequel to Skator Gator!

Tasked with cleaning up copious amounts of trash, Greenjamin Gator grabs his skateboard to dash, jump, grind, climb, and skate their way through many polluted locales.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1996470/Skator_Gator_3D/
itch.io: https://weatheredsweater.itch.io/skator-gator-3d
